I'm going to reset this margin.

00:02:57.410 --> 00:02:58.685
I'm going to click on that.

00:02:58.685 --> 00:03:00.470
And let's click on Reset.

00:03:00.470 --> 00:03:03.005
Alternatively, you can
hold down the Option or

00:03:03.005 --> 00:03:06.770
Alt key and then click
on that just like this.

00:03:06.770 --> 00:03:09.395
Alright, so how can I
align it to the center?

00:03:09.395 --> 00:03:10.760
I have different options.

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:12.560
Whenever you have
an element that has

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.390
a fixed width like this,

00:03:14.390 --> 00:03:17.075
when the width is defined here,

00:03:17.075 --> 00:03:20.105
as you can see here, the
width is 300 pixels.

00:03:20.105 --> 00:03:23.300
You can set the left and
right margin to auto.

00:03:23.300 --> 00:03:24.620
If I click on that,

00:03:24.620 --> 00:03:27.065
I can set the left
margin to auto.

00:03:27.065 --> 00:03:28.580
And then I'm going to set

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:30.905
the right margin
to auto as well.

00:03:30.905 --> 00:03:31.850
There we go.

00:03:31.850 --> 00:03:33.935
Now it's centered perfectly.

00:03:33.935 --> 00:03:35.870
Let's give it a try. I'm
going to check if it's

00:03:35.870 --> 00:03:38.150
responsive and if
it works properly,

00:03:38.150 --> 00:03:39.590
I'm going to go to tablet.

00:03:39.590 --> 00:03:42.575
As you can see, it's
still in the middle.

00:03:42.575 --> 00:03:45.335
That's perfect. Alright,
this is one option.

00:03:45.335 --> 00:03:47.870
Okay, let me reset
these margins.

00:03:47.870 --> 00:03:51.245
You could just click on
this button right here.

00:03:51.245 --> 00:03:55.085
Now both left and right
margins are set to auto.

00:03:55.085 --> 00:03:57.650
However, keep in mind
that this way only

00:03:57.650 --> 00:04:00.320
works when you have
a defined width.

00:04:00.320 --> 00:04:02.510
If not, you can use another way,

00:04:02.510 --> 00:04:04.220
and that is flexbox.

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:06.680
Alright, let me
reset this margins.

