the center and justify
it to the center.

00:04:19.100 --> 00:04:19.790
There we go.

00:04:19.790 --> 00:04:21.335
We've got the same thing,

00:04:21.335 --> 00:04:23.165
but this option works even if

00:04:23.165 --> 00:04:26.540
your element doesn't
have a defined width.

